'''Nicole Love''' is the Senior Manager of Production and Design for [[Lucas Online]], whose work includes [[StarWars.com]], [http://www.lucasarts.com LucasArts.com], [http://www.indianajones.com IndianaJones.com], [http://www.lucasfilm.com Lucasfilm.com], [http://www.ilm.com ILM.com], [http://www.skysound.com SkySound.com], [http://www.thx1138movie.com THX1138movie.com], and more.

The [[Star Wars comic books|comic strip]] ''[[Reversal of Fortune]]'' featured a character named [[Nikki Vul]], a [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Human/Legends|Human]] who worked as a [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] news reporter near the end of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. She was named after Love.

